Package com.Game.model.order

Class AirliftOrder

java.lang.Object
com.Game.model.order.Order
com.Game.model.order.AirliftOrder
Direct Known Subclasses:
AirliftAttack, AirliftMove
public abstract class AirliftOrder extends Order
Abstract class representing an airlift order in the game. An airlift order involves moving armies from one territory to another via airlift. In the Command pattern, this is a part of the concrete Command hierarchy.

    • execute

      public abstract void execute()
      Executes the airlift order. The specific implementation of the execution is defined by subclasses. In the Command pattern, this abstract method will be implemented by concrete commands.
